[[BMT牙買加線|BMT牙買加線]]上的'''百老匯交匯車站'''是快車停靠的車站，有三條軌道以及兩個[[島式月台|島式月台]]<ref name="NYCDCP-BwayJctStudy-2008" />。中間的快車軌道臨時作為M線列車總站<ref name="NYCDCP-BwayJctStudy-2008" />，在車站的兩側都有軌道連接[[纽约地铁车辆段#東紐約車廠|東紐約車輛段]]。列車可以途經此站進入車輛段，或是從車輛段途經此站進入牙買加線。

此站最早叫做'''百老匯-東園道車站'''（{{lang|en|Broadway – Eastern Parkway}}），因為其出入口在車站的極東側，該出入口已封閉，但街梯和車站屋仍然存在<ref name="NYCDCP-BwayJctStudy-2008" />。在月台中間，在大約康威街的位置曾有第二個檢票口，不過也已經封閉<ref name="NYCDCP-BwayJctStudy-2008" /><ref name=PCAC-ClosedSubwayEntrance-2001>{{cite web |title=Reopening Closed Subway Entrances |url=http://www.pcac.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/2001-Reopening-Closed-Entrances.pdf |website=pcac.org |publisher=New York City Transit Riders Council |accessdate=6 December 2015 |date=November 2001 |archive-date=2015-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222153323/http://www.pcac.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/2001-Reopening-Closed-Entrances.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，也在2000年左右拆除<ref name="NYCDCP-BwayJctStudy-2008" /><ref name="MTA-BwayJct-Rehab-1997">{{Cite web|url=http://www.mta.nyc.ny.us/mta/html/eye-nyct.htm |title=REHABILITATE EAST NEW YORK STATION COMPLEX BROOKLYN |last= |first= |date=1997-02-02 |website=mta.nyc.ny.us |publisher=[[NYCTA|New York City Transit]] |access-date=2016-09-18 |deadurl= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19970202045430/http://www.mta.nyc.ny.us/mta/html/eye-nyct.htm |archivedate=1997-02-02 }}</ref>。舊福爾頓高架鐵路軌道的鐵架可以在車站複合的月台下方部分看見。每個月台有兩條樓梯接到交匯車站較上面的夾層<ref name="NYCDCP-BwayJctStudy-2008" />。夾層在月台上方，利用兩條較長[[電扶梯|電扶梯]]連接卡納西線車站及地面層的出入口<ref name="NYCDCP-BwayJctStudy-2008" />。地面層有通道通到[[IND福爾頓街線|IND福爾頓街線]]及[[檢票口|檢票口]]<ref name="NYCDCP-BwayJctStudy-2008" />。夾層比月台要多延伸1/3的長度<ref name=NYCDCP-BwayJctStudy-2008>{{cite web|title=Broadway Junction Transportation Study: NYC Department of City Planning Final Report-November 2008|url=http://www1.nyc.gov/assets/planning/download/pdf/plans/transportation/broadway_junction_complete.pdf|website=nyc.gov|publisher=New York City Department of City Planning|accessdate=27 October 2015|date=November 2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100606140932/http://www.nyc.gov/html/dcp/pdf/transportation/broadway_junction_complete.pdf|archivedate=2010-06-06}}</ref>，是用混凝土所作的。一度有窗戶<ref name="BOT-1949">{{Cite book|url=http://hdl.handle.net/2027/mdp.39015023094926|title=Report for the three and one-half years ending June 30, 1949.|publisher=New York City Board of Transportation|date=1949}}</ref>，不過後來已經封閉。

