[[IND福爾頓街線|IND福爾頓街線]]上的百老匯交匯車站，以前稱為「百老匯-東紐約車站」（{{lang|en|Broadway–East New York}}）<ref name="NYCDCP-BwayJctStudy-2008" /><ref name="BklynEagle-BwayENY-Open-Jan1947">{{cite news|title=Little Move, but Good|url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/52675883/?terms=%22subway%22%2B%22broadway%22%2B%22east%2Bnew%2Byork%22|accessdate=15 July 2016|work=Brooklyn Daily Eagle|via=Newspapers.com|date=January 2, 1947|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220191418/https://www.newspapers.com/image/52675883/?terms=%22subway%22%2B%22broadway%22%2B%22east%2Bnew%2Byork%22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BklynEagle-BwyJct-BigEscalator-Feb1947">{{cite news|title=Big Escalator To Link Three Lines in E.N.Y.: Will connect Fulton St. Subway With 14th St., Broadway Routes|url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/52701033/?terms=%22Big%2Bescalator%22|accessdate=15 July 2016|work=Brooklyn Daily Eagle|via=Newspapers.com|date=February 17, 1947|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220191431/https://www.newspapers.com/image/52701033/?terms=%22Big%2Bescalator%22|dead-url=no}}</ref>是一個有四條軌道軌、兩個[[島式月台|島式月台]]的快車地鐵站<ref name="NYCDCP-BwayJctStudy-2008" />。

此車站在1930年代興建，在美國參與[[第二次世界大戰|第二次世界大戰]]時幾乎完工，但因為物資短缺而停工<ref name="NYCDCP-BwayJctStudy-2008" /><ref name=Raskin-RoutesNotTaken-2013 /><ref name=BklynEagle-INDFultonCulver-ShortageSnarl-1946>{{cite web|last1=Blauvelt|first1=Paul|title=Shortages Snarl $50,000,000 Tube Links|url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/57726129/?terms=euclid%2Bpitkin%2Bsubway|via=Newspapers.com|newspaper=Brooklyn Daily Eagle|accessdate=9 October 2015|page=21|date=June 9, 1946|archive-date=2016-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161026233049/https://www.newspapers.com/image/57726129/?terms=euclid%2Bpitkin%2Bsubway|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在戰後繼續施工，完成了必要的軌道及維修工程，並且興建了到BMT線的電扶梯<ref name=BklynEagle-INDFultonCulver-ShortageSnarl-1946/><ref name="BklynEagle-BwyJct-BigEscalator-Feb1947"/>。43公尺電扶梯的合約在1945年11月7日交由[[奧的斯電梯公司|奧的斯電梯公司]]負責<ref name="BklynEagle-BwyJct-BigEscalator-Feb1947"/>。此車站在1946年12月30日開始營運<ref name=Raskin-RoutesNotTaken-2013>{{cite book|author=Joseph B. Raskin|title=The Routes Not Taken: A Trip Through New York City's Unbuilt Subway System|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=CUlGCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA307|accessdate=12 August 2015|date=1 November 2013|publisher=Fordham University Press|isbn=978-0-8232-5369-2|archive-date=2017-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170109100746/https://books.google.com/books?id=CUlGCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA307|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BklynEagle-BwayENY-Open-Jan1947"/><ref>{{cite news|title='At Home' Boro Parties Top New Year's Week|url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/52917501/?terms=%22broadway%2Beast%2Bnew%2Byork%22|accessdate=16 July 2016|work=Brooklyn Daily Eagle|via=Newspapers.com|date=December 28, 1946|page=3|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220195009/https://www.newspapers.com/image/52917501/?terms=%22broadway%2Beast%2Bnew%2Byork%22|dead-url=no}}</ref>，不過電扶梯因為材料供應問題，延至1948年7月1日才完成<ref name="BklynEagle-BwyJct-BigEscalator-Feb1947"/><ref name="BOT-1949"/><ref>{{cite news|title=New York's Transit System Getting Six Otis Escalators|url=http://fultonhistory.com/highlighter/viewer/?file=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2FNewspaper%252010%2FYonkers%2520NY%2520Herald%2520Statesman%2FYonkers%2520NY%2520Herald%2520Statesman%25201947%2520Grayscale%2FYonkers%2520NY%2520Herald%2520Statesman%25201947%2520Grayscale%2520-%25203810.pdf&highlightsFile=http%3A%2F%2Ffultonhistory.com%2Fhighlighter%2Fhits%2F78082a4aa6b563edb3f71184d4512be7#page=1|accessdate=16 July 2016|work=The Herald Statesman|agency=Fultonhistory.com|date=September 22, 1947|page=4}}</ref>。同時也建立了和車站在一起的卡拉漢-凱里遊樂場<ref name="NYCDCP-BwayJctStudy-2008" /><ref name="NYCParks-CallahanKelly"/>。在1950年代早期，為了可停放11節車廂的列車，將月台長度延伸到660英呎<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bennett|first1=Charles G.|title=Transit Platforms on Lines in Queens to be Lengthened|url=http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive/pdf?res=9904E0D91E3BE23BBC4851DFB7678382659EDE|accessdate=16 July 2016|work=The New York Times|date=November 20, 1949}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Noonan|first1=Dan|title=Transit Board to Add 1 Car to Fulton St. IND Trains: 11-Car Units Will East Rush Hour Jam in Boro|url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/53773872/?terms=%22transit%2Bboard%2Bto%2Badd%2B1%2Bcar%22%2Bbroadway%2B%22east%2Bnew%2Byork%22|accessdate=16 July 2016|work=Brooklyn Daily Eagle|via=Newspapers.com|date=March 6, 1951|page=5|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220195020/https://www.newspapers.com/image/53773872/?terms=%22transit%2Bboard%2Bto%2Badd%2B1%2Bcar%22%2Bbroadway%2B%22east%2Bnew%2Byork%22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive/pdf?res=9E00E7DA153EE53BBC4051DFBE668388649EDE|title = 2 Subway Lines to Add Cars, Another to Speed Up Service|last = Ingalls|first = Leonard|date = August 28, 1953|work = |access-date = January 25, 2016|via = |newspaper = New York Times}}</ref>。

這個車站的瓷磚帶相當特別，結合了光澤和啞光的瓷磚，其中在邊緣有鈷藍色的光澤，中間部份則是藍莓色的啞光部份。車站在2003年更名，牆上瓷磚上的EASTAN改為對應字形的JUNCTION。在往皇后區一側的月台有一個仍運作中的控制塔<ref name="NYTimes-INDEuclid-NX-1948">{{cite news|title=Buttons to Speed Travel in Subway: $2,000,000 System of Signals Soon to Be in Operation on Brooklyn IND Division|url=http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive/pdf?res=950DE3D6143DEE3ABC4A52DFB7678383659EDE|accessdate=27 December 2016|work=The New York Times|date=November 12, 1948|archive-date=2018-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180212104229/http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive/pdf?res=950DE3D6143DEE3ABC4A52DFB7678383659EDE|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在車站的東側，隧道往左右两侧擴展，配合區間軌分支出來的額外軌道。這個鐘口是為了計劃中、延長[[BMT牙買加線|BMT牙買加線]]的延伸線而設計，或是為了另一個計劃中的{{le|牙買加大道|Jamaica Avenue}}地鐵而設計<ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9FiS6X83UvM {{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9FiS6X83UvM |date=20170810225416 }} ''The bellmouth can be seen towards the right, at the 5:40 mark in the video, just before the train enters the Broadway Junction station.''</ref>。這個钟口不是為了{{link-en|紐約地鐵擴建計劃|Proposed expansion of the New York City Subway|IND第二系統}}所預備，其年代可以追溯到較早期的IND福尔顿街线計劃，當時是將此車站以西的軌道和此車站東邊的二條線連接：BMT牙买加线以及到[[臭氧公園-勒弗茲林蔭路車站_(IND福爾頓街線)|勒弗茲林蔭路車站]]BMT福尔顿街线（最後還是在[[格蘭特大道車站_(IND福爾頓街線)|格蘭特大道車站]]連到IND福尔顿街线）<ref>{{cite news|title=New Fulton St Subway Officially Started  as Byrne Turns Earth|url=http://bklyn.newspapers.com/clip/7728577//|date=April 17, 1929|page=4}}</ref>。其中一個鐘口是緊急出口。

